QED</link> <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../310/30310.xml">
text editor</link> was first implemented by Butler Lampson and L. Peter Deutsch for the Berkeley Timesharing System in 1967.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%223%22])">3</ref></p>

